<html>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.6;">
    <h2>Your Lab Result is Ready</h2>
    <p>Hi {{patientName}},</p>
    <p>The result for sample <strong>{{sampleId}}</strong> is now available.</p>
    <p><strong>Test:</strong> {{testName}}</p>
